data.description: Welcome to 9108 Parlor Drive! This gorgeous  townhome boasts 3 bedrooms, 3.5 bathrooms, with 2,617 sq ft on 3 stories in the quiet community of Tranquil Hill Plantation in Ladson. As you enter you'll notice the 2 story entryway with soaring ceilings and tons of natural light. The first of two family rooms is on the first floor. It could be used as a mother in law suite with its full bath and walk in shower, for your family as another hangout spot or a great space to entertain. Fantastic covered porch in the back to relax and take in the lowcountry beauty. Lovely Cherry hardwood floors throughout the main living area, tile on the first floor family room, vinyl in the laundry room and all of the full bathrooms.Wall to wall carpet on the stairs, hallways and bedrooms, Corian countertops in the kitchen, a stainless steel undermount sink, stainless dishwasher and side by side fridge, a black flat top electric range and microwave. Most of the appliances are less than 2 years old. The washer, dryer and 42'' LED flat screen tv are all included with this home. Beautiful Cherry 42" cabinets in the kitchen with a large pantry, two eating areas, formal dining/living room and a separate informal space for everyday living. Owner's suite has a garden tub, a separate shower along with a walk in closet. One of the two balconies is off the owner's suite in the rear of the home and the other is off the kitchen and casual dining room. Large 2 car garage for all of your storage needs. You won't need a lawnmower here because the landscaping is done for you! Relax by the pool and enjoy the Southern Charm with the Live Oaks and Rainbow Row colored homes. Close to shopping, dining, only 10 minutes to Downtown Summerville and 45 minutes to the beaches. Oakbrook Elementary and Middle schools are just down the road. HOA covers insurance, roofs, landscaping, pool, termite bond, exterior building maintenance and the homes get power washed every other year.
